title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Afters with Kyle Ng
description:
On our new weekly lightning round mini ep with Kyle Ng, we’re fucking around with hobbies, hyphy, LA, brunch fits, Erewhon, change, comic books, Magic: The Gathering, superheroes, superpowers, horror, Trump merch and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
